title: Dems Celebrate Afghanistan, Inflation
description: Fellas discuss the latest news as Dems celebrate Afghanistan, high prices and IRS agents. U.S. Army veteran and Congressman Mike Waltz joins the progrum for a conversation about Afghanistan. Former Rep. Devin Nunes also joins for an interview.
author: hello@ruthlesspodcast.com (Mike Waltz, Devin Nunes, Comfortably Smug, John Ashbrook, Josh Holmes, Michael Duncan)
